¼This flowerbed
was added to this lovely garden
by
Forward 4 Work
(helping local people with disabilities into work)
on Rosie Day 12th May 2009.
These flowers have been planted in
loving memory of those we have lost and for the
wonderful work of nurses everywhere on
International Nurses Day."ų
ėIn memory of
MICHAEL JOHN EDWYN GOLD
Born bred and contentedly
laid peacefully to rest
within the place he vehemently loved.
He is sadly missed and fondly remembered
by all the Family and Friends
fortunate enough to hare known Mike,
who remains an integral component of
Maxstoke and its history.
25th March 1932 - 14th April 2013"ū
